# New Lesson Checklist

Use when adding a **new module**, a **new doc type** for an existing lesson (plain-language, quick study, quiz), or doing a **major lesson expansion** that needs site-wide updates.

## 1. Content

- [ ] Full guide follows patterns in `docs/lesson-03/intradomain-routing.md` (or flat `lesson-NN-<topic>.md`)
- [ ] Study questions from Canvas addressed (as `##` headings in full guide or in quick study Q&A)
- [ ] Cross-links to prior/next lessons (e.g., Lesson 3 ↔ Lesson 4 for IGP/BGP)
- [ ] Course references line: Module N Summary Video, Kurose & Ross chapters

## 2. Sibling docs (if applicable)

| Adding… | Also check |
|---------|------------|
| Full guide | Should plain-language / quick study / quiz be created or linked as "coming soon"? |
| plain-language | Links to full guide; covers same core concepts simplified |
| Quick study | Numbered sections + exam Q&A + memory sheet |
| Quiz | YAML frontmatter + `<quiz>` blocks aligned with quick study |

Update **cross-links in all existing siblings** when adding a new format.

## 3. Site navigation

- [ ] `mkdocs.yml` → add under correct lesson in `nav:` (match nesting of Lessons 1–3)
- [ ] `docs/index.md` → Modules table row + Practice table if plain-language/quiz/quick study
- [ ] No orphan pages — every new `docs/*.md` must appear in nav or redirect stub

## 4. Images

- [ ] New diagrams saved to `docs/images/lesson-NN/kebab-case-name.png`
- [ ] Referenced from `docs/lesson-NN/*.md` as `![descriptive alt](../images/lesson-NN/kebab-case-name.png)`
- [ ] Reuse existing images when the same course diagram applies

## 5. Build verification

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
mkdocs build
```

Fix any broken links, missing images, or quiz syntax errors before finishing.

## 6. Related pages

- [ ] `docs/practice-questions.md` — add written Q&A if module has official study questions not yet covered

## Filename conventions

```
docs/lesson-NN/
  <topic>.md          # full guide (descriptive name)
  plain-language.md
  quick-study-guide.md
  quiz.md
```

Match `mkdocs.yml` nav. Do not recreate flat `lesson-NN-*.md` files at `docs/` root — content lives only in `docs/lesson-NN/`.
